# Five Parsecs Campaign Manager - Development Guidelines

This document provides comprehensive development guidelines for the Five Parsecs Campaign Manager project, a digital adaptation of the Five Parsecs from Home tabletop game built in Godot 4.4.

## Project Overview

The Five Parsecs Campaign Manager is a digital campaign management tool that implements the complete ruleset from Five Parsecs from Home. The project follows a modular architecture with clear separation between base abstractions, core systems, and game-specific implementations.

### Key Systems Status
- ✅ **Story Track System** - Production ready (20/20 tests passing)
- ✅ **Battle Events System** - Production ready (22/22 tests passing)
- ✅ **Digital Dice System** - Production ready with visual interface
- ✅ **Campaign Manager** - Enhanced integration layer

